4. Top with the grated tomatoes.

🕷Spooky Spider Dip🕸
This easy black bean dip comes together fast to create a festive dip perfect for your Halloween parties! 
👉 Blend 1 can of drained black beans with 1/4 cup water, 2 teaspoons smoked paprika, 1 teaspoon cumin, and 1 tablespoon fresh lime juice. Blend until creamy. Add salt if needed. 
👉Spread dip out in a serving dish. 
👉Place sour cream in a sandwich bag and cut off the corner. Pipe circles on top of dip.
👉Use a toothpick to make the web.
👉Top with a spider
👉Serve with chips
